      "span_text": "Define T (G) as the set of all directed spanning trees for a graph G. As  noted, there is a one-to-one correspondence between spanning trees of G x and labeled dependency graphs of x, i.e., T (G x ) is exactly the set of all possible projective and non-projective dependency graphs for sentence x.",
